_sText:
This isn't really a serious map, just made it for a bit of fun. It's rather small 12 people max per side. Tele's have the half life symbol to tell you they're there. Also do not crouch when you jump down the hole, you'll just die. You'll know what i mean when you play it. There are two hidden tele's to get to an open vantage point. Hope you enjoy,
               BluR
